Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有聽到什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果落下去了  在這樣的暴風雨救上來是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還只是個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼簡單的放棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能那麼簡單的就死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣死心的話  不就相當於自己認輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要變得和爸爸說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離家出走是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:57.02,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流到了  天國!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就做美味的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天有暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會有很大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  那麼快就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得…確實被大浪吞噬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:44.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你  振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死  把水排出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這種時候最後的手段是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再發生什麼真的要下地獄了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什什什什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是地獄  這是…天國…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有好好按照所學的人工呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（去天國）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像外面的人漂流到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想救他卻給他致命一擊是想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪  明明按照婆婆所說的那樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是外人第一次漂流到這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很少見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子和我們有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部也平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不同  想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為呐  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好重  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這個那個都偷懶不工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子是男孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子會變得很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  沒關…不會沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不單救了我  連飯都準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫東方院行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃不喝一周漂流到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連你也在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我還以為漂流到了相當遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好還是在日本裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實住在這裡的都是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島在哪裡可不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為  其實我們也是漂流到了這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是距現在130年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本開國後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為了學習最新的技術和醫學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,駛向歐洲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆您貴庚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是途中碰到大風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然就漂流到了這個島上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慶幸的是這個島容易居住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,取了和沉沒的船一樣的名字  叫藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣生活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還有這樣的島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看你身穿的裝飾  日本也改變的相當的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有離開島的船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣怎麼才能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在別想多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在鈴家裡慢慢的養傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以後的事情以後考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用船到附近的島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡也許會有聯絡船或飛機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  剛才就在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子是炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時讓你睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上讓你好好吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在很忙  沒空和你玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別把人說的好像很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要住在鈴家比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴家非常的破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屋頂破了會漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蟲子老鼠一堆堆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  鈴睡相很差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還會尿床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種差勁的攻擊  對我是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼走吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以嗎  那樣放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種程度  綾音沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故意被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在後面  找尋敵人的破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中我的計謀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然身體還麻痹著  還過得去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多被打中幾次就會習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不想習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音她從小就和我針鋒相對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事就來找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負倒還好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我是否願意這一點  還真為難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說起來  你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家雙親都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  問了不該問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還真為難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和女孩一起  兩人同住一個屋簷下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行  不能想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那麼我也進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…鈴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  幫你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…我已經洗過了  不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡大家相互搓背了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相互搓背？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平常女生能無所謂的和男生一起進浴室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人  舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也許就是島上的風俗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,這回輪到行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣我也平靜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是從哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想來擦洗行人大人的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到每一寸肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那由我來做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上  像你這樣的小鬼  真的能讓男士滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說小鬼還真失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音你也不是又矮又平的  像小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不得不和你做一回了斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  熱得暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  冷水拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我來帶你參觀這個島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事無所謂  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  公子  還真危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  綾音那傢伙竟然偷跑  還真不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是木匠玲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說回來  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  那個  我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做我的丈…丈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  為什麼這麼簡單的事情說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是漂流到島上的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子…我可不想被小孩子說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把淑女說成小孩是侮辱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃深受打擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要  不要  不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣  作為賠禮  今天和雪乃約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  那邊的公子是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這早熟的小鬼  還早十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子是雪乃的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不逃的話  就要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要儘快離開這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你準備的很豐盛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞞著鈴出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說被綁架出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎感覺到了殺氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你在為難什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還是白天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我叫千影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…感覺很懂禮貌  這是個正常的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一樣的手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,躲過了我的吹箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是不同的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  連射式？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼有趣的研究物件  可不能讓你逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊  上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都要追著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人是婆婆叫我照看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是這樣說  你卻是想自己獨佔男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也想和鈴一樣跟他約會  親熱什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那種事情沒做過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,親熱又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底  大家這麼圍著人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島上沒有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除你以外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這全是女人的島上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就我一個男的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾條命都不夠的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然鈴照顧了我許多  但我還是決定要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追我追的那麼厲害的人  還真這麼容易就放我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍蘭島嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然受了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看還真是美麗的島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎  讓他走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他自身體驗是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島的周圍都被漩渦所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到不了外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想從我的手裡逃出去是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…頭冒星星  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅靠自己要出這島是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼努力絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行的  放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去做過怎麼會知道！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼想做的話  先把我打倒了再去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然做不到的話  就別說大話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的「絕對不行」已經囉嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  我會死心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼試都沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你超越不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人  要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說是絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要做了比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣亂來下去  不單單只是受重傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只看出我到現在都被打飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我有好好的用身體記住漩渦的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼失敗  人所做的事情沒有一樣是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是爺爺的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經看穿這一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的已經完全改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡做無意義的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,認真倔強的男人真是不討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明連什麼是男人都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會成功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  那邊不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  如我所想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漩渦和漩渦之間有間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈～  看到了嗎  這回是我的勝利…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虎…虎鯨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  這傢伙是來妨礙我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  一個又一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想做什麼的時候總會有礙事的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經忍不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣受別人做主的人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不想打到你～的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好運  現在的話能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  已經沒有力氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來…了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果…我還是什麼都沒做成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這深海裡  成為虎鯨的飼料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是來救我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生魚片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生魚片是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些漩渦外面的地方  有最大的激流漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且任何東西都會被捲裂  吸入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生魚片是為了不讓任何人接近而巡視著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
